graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:BplusItSappiCreateJobDetailInput!)
{
	bplusItSappiCreateJobDetail (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		systemId
		systemName
		executionId
		executionType
		executionExecutedAt
		executionMonitoringStartAt
		executionMonitoringEndAt
		status
		detail
		example
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
